  "notes": "Live 2026-04 evidence shows metafieldsSet stores `$app:<suffix>` and omitted namespaces under the current app's canonical namespace, canonical owner reads observe those values, metafieldsDelete resolves `$app:<suffix>` before deleting the canonical metafield, and canonical namespaces owned by another API client return payload-level userErrors on the namespace-taking value mutation roots. The singular metafieldDelete root is retained as a local compatibility alias but modern Shopify capture evidence is necessarily on metafieldsDelete because the live schema no longer exposes a namespace-taking singular root."
